items.name: Crossy-Road-Style-Game
items.description: 🛣️ Isometric Endless Runner: A simple road-crossing game similar to Crossy Road. 🎮 Focuses on procedural level loading dan 3D-like isometric rendering. 📐 🚦

items.name: Pac-Man-Maze-Adventure
items.description: 👻 Retro Maze Runner: A faithful recreation of Pac-Man. 🟡 Focuses on complex AI pathfinding for ghosts dan precise maze geometry management. 🗺️

items.name: AI-Art-Generator
items.description: 🎨 AI Art Generator: A project using generative models (GANs, Diffusion) to create images from text prompts. 🤖 Explores the intersection of AI dan creativity. 🖼️

items.name: WeatherWise-App
items.description: 🌤️ Atmospheric Forecast: A WeatherWise application that pulls real-time weather data dan 5-day forecasts from external APIs. 🌍 Focuses on clean, modern data visualization. 📊 ☁️

items.name: ChatConnect-Realtime
items.description: 🔗 Real-time Communication Engine: Core networking engine for low-latency message delivery using WebSockets. 💬 Separated for modular backend services. 📡 🌐

items.name: 2D-Platformer
items.description: 🏃 2D Platformer: A basic side-scrolling runner template. 🍄 Complete with jumping physics, gravity simulation, dan collectible items. Great template for game design. 🏰 🌟

items.name: Cross-Platform-App-Shell
items.description: 📱 Cross-Platform-App-Shell: A boilerplate project for building mobile apps that run on both iOS dan Android. ⚡ Uses a framework like React Native atau Flutter. 🚀

items.name: ETL-Pipeline-Framework
items.description: 🔩 ETL Pipeline Framework: A framework for building Extract, Transform, Load (ETL) pipelines. 📦 Moves dan processes data from various sources to a data warehouse. 🚚

items.name: Web3-Minting-Platform
items.description: 🖼️ Web3-Minting-Platform: A decentralized application (DApp) for minting NFTs on a test network. A great introduction to Web3 dan smart contract development. ⛓️

items.name: Breakout-Game
items.description: 🏓 Brick Breaker Arcade: A recreation of Breakout featuring complex ball trajectory physics. 🎯 Excellent for mastering game loops dan advanced level design. 💥

items.name: LearningLighthouse-Platform

items.name: Memory-Test
items.description: 🧠 Memory Test: A cognitive memory test game designed to measure dan improve short-term memory. 💡 Uses sequences atau pattern recognition challenges. Focuses on performance tracking. ⏱️ 📈

items.name: Simple-Blockchain-Impl
items.description: 🔗 Simple Blockchain Impl: A simplified, educational implementation of a blockchain from scratch. ⛓️ Demonstrates concepts like hashing, blocks, dan proof-of-work. 💡

items.name: Grid-Matrix-Game
items.description: 🧱 Grid-Matrix-Game: A meticulous adaptation of Tetris. 🧠 Focuss on complex block rotation, line clearing logic, dan high-performance rendering. ⚙️

items.name: Metroidvania-Game
items.description: 🏰 Action-Adventure Mapping: A Metroidvania style game focusing on interconnected map design. 🗺️ Features item progression dan combat mechanics. Complex dan rewarding development. ⚔️ 🗝️

items.name: Asteroids-Game
items.description: ☄️ Space Shooter Classic: An Asteroids recreation featuring angular velocity dan thrust physics. 🛰️ Manages complex projectile behavior. A foundational project for game development. 💥 🌠

items.name: Sentiment-Analysis-API
items.description: 📈 Sentiment Analysis API: A web API that analyzes text dan returns its sentiment (positive, negative, neutral). 🧠 Built with a pre-trained NLP model. 📊

items.name: Online-Store
items.description: 🛒 Online Store: A basic e-commerce shop frontend. 🛍️ Displays products, carts, dan basic checkout flow without complex backend integration. Focuses on UI/UX design. 📦 💳

items.name: Code-Runner-Game
items.description: 🧠 Code Runner Game: A coding puzzle game where users solve short coding challenges. 💻 Runs puzzles directly within the game environment. Focuses on algorithmic thinking dan execution sandboxing. 🧪 🚀

items.name: MQTT-Broker-Client
items.description: 📲 MQTT Broker Client: A client application for publishing dan subscribing to an MQTT broker. 📡 The cornerstone of IoT communication protocols.

items.name: My-Library-App

items.name: VR-World-Builder
items.description: 🕶️ VR-World-Builder: A basic template for creating a simple Virtual Reality (VR) scene. 🌍 A great starting point for Oculus atau WebVR development. 🕹️
